entry.title: First Post "Hello World"
entry.summary:
The beginning of something wonderful

"Hello World" was popularized as a "learning the basics" part of programming and it does just that! It funcations as a verification that the systems are functioning and serves as a humble reminder of where we all start.

Be Humble
